15:05.300 --> 15:07.295
How do you know
all of these things?

15:07.297 --> 15:09.664
Well, it's common knowledge.

15:09.666 --> 15:11.030
Well..

15:11.032 --> 15:13.865
Oh, I'm going to Japan.

15:15.665 --> 15:18.130
