after the season.

15:18.132 --> 15:21.364
Oh, Moe, I have always
wanted to see Japan.

15:21.366 --> 15:23.032
I'll take some pictures.

15:23.034 --> 15:26.596
Or you could take me, and I'll
take the pictures myself.

15:26.598 --> 15:29.763
- Oh, Estella, come on.
- I'd really like to go, Moe.

15:29.765 --> 15:33.330
It's just a series
of exhibition games.

15:33.332 --> 15:35.396
And I'm sure the other players
are taking their wives.

15:35.398 --> 15:37.498
You're not my wife.

15:43.432 --> 15:44.530
Mm.

15:44.532 --> 15:45.665
I didn't mean
anything by that.

15:45.667 --> 15:48.363
I was simply stating it
as a fact.

15:48.365 --> 15:49.429
It was more than that, Moe.

15:49.431 --> 15:50.896
It wasn't more than anything.

15:50.898 --> 15:52.898
- <i>Estella.</i>
- What?

15:54.599 --> 15:56.665
Why do you not want
to take me to Japan, Morris?

16:01.531 --> 16:03.897
I would just rather go alone.

16:07.765 --> 16:10.400
Well, that wasn't so hard,
