18:47.863 --> 18:48.995
- Oh!
- Oh!

18:49.598 --> 18:51.562
[audience applauding]

18:52.398 --> 18:53.895
[bells tolling]

18:53.897 --> 18:55.163
[ducks quacking]

18:58.530 --> 19:02.096
Please, tell me
all about baseball.

19:02.098 --> 19:05.030
