understand, Mr. Berg.

19:38.730 --> 19:40.828
This visit is very important.

19:41.663 --> 19:43.763
It goes beyond sport.

19:45.198 --> 19:48.795
Our cultures are very different,
and growing further apart.

19:50.596 --> 19:54.427
If we don't stop to learn
about one another, then..

19:54.429 --> 19:55.894
Then what?

19:57.528 --> 19:59.261
There'll be no more games.

20:04.664 --> 20:07.796
