20:24.364 --> 20:25.829
Why?

20:30.463 --> 20:32.595
<i>When I was growing up</i>

20:32.597 --> 20:35.027
<i>my first baseball team
was a church team.</i>

20:35.029 --> 20:36.461
<i>But I'm a Jew.</i>

20:36.463 --> 20:38.795
<i>Now, I was never
a practicing Jew</i>

20:38.797 --> 20:42.729
but I was different
than the other boys.

20:42.731 --> 20:44.362
I never even told them
my real name.

20:44.364 --> 20:46.130
I tried to blend in.

20:47.163 --> 20:49.128
I wanted to hide.

20:49.130 --> 20:50.595
And it worked.

20:50.597 --> 20:52.529
Do you like to hide, Mr. Berg?

20:54.930 --> 20:56.028
I do.

20:56.030 --> 20:57.162
[chuckles]

20:58.895 --> 21:00.161
I don't fit.

21:02.795 --> 21:06.728
Even now, I have no real home,
I have no wife.

21:11.229 --> 21:12.895
Do you have a wife, Isao?

21:13.429 --> 21:14.694
I do.

21:14.696 --> 21:17.260
And six children.

21:17.262 --> 21:19.029
She's very fertile.

21:22.030 --> 21:24.760
I like to hide too.

21:24.762 --> 21:27.894
[instrumental music]

21:38.530 --> 21:39.994
[sighs]

21:51.163 --> 21:53.527
Now, can I ask you
an important question?

21:53.529 --> 21:55.294
Yes.

21:55.296 --> 21:57.827
You're a professor of history.

21:57.829 --> 22:00.594
Will there be a war
between our two countries?

22:00.596 --> 22:02.261
[music continues]

22:08.329 --> 22:09.395
Yes.

22:10.995 --> 22:13.662
It has been progressing
step-by-step.

22:14.528 --> 22:16.061
It is quite inevitable.

22:18.828 --> 22:20.394
<i>Everything will change.</i>

22:23.262 --> 22:25.863
<i>And we'll all play our part.</i>

22:29.327 --> 22:32.061
I also think
after this visit..

22:34.563 --> 22:36.294
