see each other again.

22:39.830 --> 22:41.963
I hope you're wrong.

22:45.529 --> 22:47.394
As do I.

22:47.396 --> 22:50.328
[music continues]

23:17.493 --> 23:20.227
[music continues]

23:39.161 --> 23:41.094
