23:46.295 --> 23:50.461
<i>The attack yesterday
on the Hawaiian Islands</i>

23:50.463 --> 23:53.293
<i>has caused severe damage</i>

23:53.295 --> 23:57.291
<i>to American naval
and military forces.</i>

23:57.293 --> 24:00.993
